name: EONSphere #2 "Our Brief Moment"
description: MP4, 3840x2160, Ed 1/1, 2021. The EONSpheres are 4 reprojection fragments from EONS (https://miketyka.com/?p=eons), a 2019 short animation film made by @mtyka, created entirely using neural networks. Our presence on this planet has been but a tiny moment in the eons of geological time. And yet, despite all our accumulated scientific knowledge, we are incapable of truly understanding the vastness of this history and our insignificance in it. #TheFEN
